  "text": "The value of biochemical components are shown in Table 4 . The range of FFA value at different treatments was 0.32 to 0.33% and 0.32 to 0.34% for days intervals. Similar results also found in the study of [CITATION_1] . During storage, the POV increased in all treatments. 0.10 ± 0.00 0.11 ± 0.00 0.11 ± 0.00 0.11 ± 0.00 0.10 a ± 0.00 30 0.11 ± 0.00 0.11 ± 0.00 0.11 ± 0.00 0.11 ± 0.00 0.11 a ± 0.00 60 0.11 ± 0.00 0.11 ± 0.00 0.11 ± 0.00 0.11 ± 0.00 0.11 a ± 0.00 Mean 0.10 a ± 0.00 011 a ± 0.00 0.11 a ± 0.00 011 a ± 0.00",
